=begin
Last run FirebaseInstanceID installed:
* FirebaseCore (5.4.0)
* FirebaseInstanceID (3.8.0)
* GoogleUtilities (5.5.0)

Check if main version or subversion number has changed. 
If yes, please, update *.targets file located in binding 
project, also, update Podfile file if needed.

In Firebase.InstanceID binding project, you can find the Native Reference of:
* FirebaseInstanceID (3.8.0)

In Firebase.Core binding project, you can find the Native Reference of:
* FirebaseCore (5.4.0)
* GoogleUtilities (5.5.0)
=end

source 'https://github.com/CocoaPods/Specs.git'

platform :ios, '8.0'
install! 'cocoapods', :integrate_targets => false
use_frameworks!

=begin
This override the static_framework flag to false,
in order to be able to build dynamic frameworks.
=end
pre_install do |installer|
	installer.pod_targets.each do |pod|
		def pod.static_framework?;
			false
		end
	end
end

target 'FirebaseInstanceID' do
	pod 'FirebaseInstanceID', '3.8.0'
end
